        <briefdescription>
<para>Lock the 1-wire bus to prevent simultaneous access. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This routine locks the bus to prevent simultaneous access from different threads. The calling thread waits until the bus becomes available. A thread is permitted to lock a mutex it has already locked.</para>
